word_mean_info__list.difference: 指专门从事治牙的医生。
指专修外科或专修人体某个部分的外科专科医生，这种医生一般需对患者进行手术治疗。
普通用词，泛指各科医生，即一切有行医资格的人。

bilingual.source: She never goes to the dentist for teeth cleaning.
bilingual.target: 她从不去看牙医清洁牙齿。

bilingual.source: When he was a child, Uthman wanted to be a dentist.
bilingual.target: 乌斯曼小时候想成为一名牙医。

bilingual.source: Linda is a dentist, but she does not work with people.
bilingual.target: 琳达是牙医，但她不与人一起工作。

bilingual.source: I am afraid of going to the dentist.

list.abstract: dentist（英[ˈdentɪst]，美[ˈdentɪst]），英语单词。词性是名词，释义为牙医。例句：You' d better go to the dentist's now.（你最好现在就去看牙医）。 近义词为dental surgeon。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait, your, your mother is sleeping with your dentist?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你妈和你的牙医上床吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa, George, the dentist will see you now. Hooray. This is Dr. Elephant, the dentist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇，乔治，轮到你们做检查啦。太好啦！这位是牙医，大象先生。

yingyinNormal.en: George, are your teeth clean like mine? It is George's first visit to the dentist. You both have lovely clean teeth, I am sure the dentist will be very happy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，你的和我的一样干净吗？这是乔治第一次去看牙医。你们的牙齿又白又干净，我相信牙医会很高兴的。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, then, just shout when you hear the task you want to undertake. Dentist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，听到你想接的任务时就吼一声。看牙医。

yingyinNormal.en: Former dentist. I need a new one now that I know where his hands have been.
yingyinNormal.zh: 前牙医，我要换一个，我知道他的手摸过"什么"了。

yingyinNormal.en: Girls, I want you to meet Mr Gru. He's going to adopt you. And he's a dentist!
yingyinNormal.zh: 姑娘们 来见见格鲁先生。他是来收养你们的，他是牙医哦！

yingyinNormal.en: I'm starting to get a sense of it. Don't worry. I'll take you to the dentist tomorrow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经开始有所体会了，别担心，我明天带你去看牙医。

yingyinNormal.en: We're gonna make this tank so filthy the dentist will have to clean it. Good work!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们要搞的这个水箱脏到那个牙医不得不清理的地步。干得好!

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, well, Bernadette's a little under the weather and my mom's kind of under my dentist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天气转凉，伯纳黛特身体不适，我妈则被我的牙医压在了身下。

yingyinNormal.en: My mom's been kind of an emotional wreck since that dentist she was dating dumped her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我妈被之前好上的那牙医抛弃之后，心情就落到了谷底，郁郁寡欢。

yingyinNormal.en: Every morning Peppa and George brush their teeth. Today Peppa and George are going to the dentist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每天早上佩奇和乔治都会刷牙。今天牙医会检查他们的牙齿。

yingyinNormal.en: Howard doesn't make me do his shopping or take him to the dentist or pick up his dry cleaning, right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍华德就不会叫我帮他买东西，送他去看牙医，帮他拿干洗的衣服，对吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Now can you show me your teeth? George does not want to show the dentist his teeth. George, open wide, like this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在让我来看看你的牙齿？乔治不想让牙医检查牙齿。乔治，张开嘴，像这样。就是这样。

yingyinNormal.en: I saved you a dumpling. Oh, your concern for me is touching. It will serve you well when you take me to the dentist tomorrow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我给你留了个饺子。你对我的关心真叫人感动，等你明天载我去看牙医我再好好报答你。

yingyinNormal.en: The water jet please, Ms. Rabbit. The dentist uses water to clean Mr. Dinosaur's teeth. The polisher, please, Ms. Rabbit. This would be a bit noisy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请准备洗牙机。牙医用水来清洁牙齿。请准备抛光机，兔小姐。可能会有点吵哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are at the dentist's waiting for their check-up. Waiting is boring. This magazine's very interesting. It's all about potatoes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和乔治来到牙医诊所等着做检查。一直等好无聊啊。这个杂志真的是太有趣了。全都是关于马铃薯的。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyhow, when you guys wake up and smell the sulfur, here's a list of other realtors, and if you need me, I'll be in the office at 9:00, 10:00. I have the dentist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总之，如果你们能清醒过来闻到硫磺的味道，这是其它地产经纪的名单如果想找我，我九点上班还是十点吧，我要去看牙医。

yingyinNormal.en: I shower twice a day and wash my hands as often as I can. Really? So do I. But you're a dentist. He's nuts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我每天洗两次澡，洗手无数次。真的？我也是。但你是牙科学生，他只是疯子。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe you can hold Mr. Dinosaur while the dentist looks at your teeth. Dinosaur. Very please to meet you, Mr. Dinosaur.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许你可以抱着恐龙先生。恐龙。很高兴见到你，恐龙先生。
